title: Panel, late 18th or early 19th century
medium: Oil on canvas, papier mache, gilded wood (frame)
description: Square panel with chinoiserie scene of man in sedan chair carried by attendants; men bowing down to him; in background, Chinaman watching scene, leaning on wall in front of fanciful pavilion.  Panel in gilt wood frame.

tombstone.epitaph:
Panel, late 18th or early 19th century.
late 18th or early 19th century. Oil on canvas, papier mache, gilded wood (frame). Gift of Neil Sellin. 1975-59-2.
